user_prompt:
Title: "Harmony Unveiled: Nature's Geometric Beauty"

Blend of Two Styles: - Minimalistic and Surreal Ink Drawing, One-Line, accentuated by alcohol-ink drawing | - Photorealistic, Low Angle Photography, Low-Key Photography | 

Artists: Erik Johannson, Tsutomu Nihei, Alejandro Burdisio, and Kim Jung Gi |

Theme: Create a visually stunning composition that seamlessly melds surreal elements of nature with a photorealistic approach, accentuated by dynamic geometric wireframes that explore the intricate beauty found in the convergence of nature and geometry in motion. |

Composition:
Foreground: Craft a photorealistic representation of a serene, mystical forest bathed in the soft, golden glow of a setting sun. The trees should appear to dance with an otherworldly grace, their branches forming fluid, organic patterns that hint at geometric precision. |
